      action: "Competitive inhibitor of xanthine oxidase, the enzyme that converts hypoxanthine to xanthine and xanthine to uric acid; its active metabolite oxypurinol has a long half-life (18-30 hours) providing sustained inhibition; reduces both serum and urinary uric acid levels",
